1. *Morao* je da se mnogo trudi da bi uspeo. (He had to work hard to succeed.)
2. On je *morao* da promeni svoje navike. (He had to change his habits.)
3. *Morala* je da se prilagodi novim okolnostima. (She had to adapt to the new circumstances.)
4. *Morali* smo da prihvatimo činjenicu. (We had to accept the fact.)
5. *Moralo* se nešto preduzeti. (Something had to be done.)